data.name: BOQ Money Market Deposit Account Fixed term
data.description: A minimum investment amount of $5,000 with lodgement terms between 31 days and 5 years. Offering terms and fixed rates of interest.

features.additionalInfo: Access to a range of Broker/Adviser features

eligibility.additionalInfo: A citizen or permanent resident of Australia
Be at least 18 years of age

fees.name: Government Charges - Interest Withholding tax (non-residents)
fees.additionalInfo: 10% of interest earned. Withheld from interest (or other amounts customer earns) amounts where customer is a non-resident. Fee charged at the same frequency of interest payment i.e., Monthly / quarterly / semi-annually / at maturity / annually (terms >1 year only)

fees.name: Break Cost
fees.additionalInfo: The greater of $100 or an adjustment to interest (See Terms & Conditions section 2.7(b))

fees.name: Government Charges - TFN withholding tax
fees.additionalInfo: 47% of interest earned. Withheld from interest amounts (or other amounts customer earns) where customer chooses not to disclose TFN. Fee charged at the same frequency of interest payment i.e., Monthly / quarterly / semi-annually / at maturity / annually (terms >1 year only)

fees.name: Repeat Statement
fees.additionalInfo: (extra copies of Statements already issued) Mailed, Emailed or Faxed Via Online Services

fees.name: Repeat Confirmation
fees.additionalInfo: (extra copies of Confirmations already issued) Mailed, Emailed or Faxed Via Online Services
